  "text": "◮ Qreg a qubit = a register [CITATION_1] ; selects the fourth qubit from a register ◮ Qreg a subreg = a register [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ; selects 5 qubits starting at the third one ◮ Qreg new reg = a subreg & a qubit;",
